      <p>Answers to key questions about our Primary school program.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>What are the age requirements?</strong> Our Primary school serves learners aged 5 to 11 years old.</li>
        <li><strong>What is the class size?</strong> We keep class sizes manageable to ensure focused teaching and support.</li>
        <li><strong>What safety measures are in place?</strong> Our campus is secure, with attentive staff, safe facilities, and clear health protocols.</li>
        <li><strong>How do you support learning differences?</strong> Teachers provide differentiated instruction and extra support where needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Can parents stay involved?</strong> Yes, we welcome parent-teacher communication, regular reports, and school events.</li>
      </ul>
